

# Storacha Space Architecture in SplitFare

## The Two Space Types

```
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│                  STORACHA SPACES                     │
│                                                     │
│  ┌───────────────────────────────────┐              │
│  │   PLATFORM SPACE (1 total)        │              │
│  │   Owner: Server-side agent        │              │
│  │                                   │              │
│  │   Contains:                       │              │
│  │   • User avatars                  │              │
│  │   • Platform-level assets         │              │
│  └───────────────────────────────────┘              │
│                                                     │
│  ┌───────────────────────────────────┐              │
│  │   GROUP SPACE (1 per group)       │              │
│  │   Name: splitfare-group-{groupId} │              │
│  │   DID stored in: Group.spaceDid   │              │
│  │                                   │              │
│  │   Contains:                       │              │
│  │   • Group avatar                  │              │
│  │   • Expense receipts              │              │
│  │   • Settlement manifests          │              │
│  │   • Shared media (photos/docs)    │              │
│  │   • CAR bundles (group archives)  │              │
│  └───────────────────────────────────┘              │
│        × N groups                                   │
└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
```

---

## Space 1: Platform Space (Single, Server-Owned)

Created once during initial deployment in **PR #5**.

Owned by the **server-side Storacha agent**.

| Content | Uploaded From | PR |
|---|---|---|
| User avatars | Server (after client crop) | #10 |

This space exists because user avatars are **not group-specific** — a user exists before joining any group. The server agent manages this space directly, no delegation needed.

---

## Space 2: Per-Group Spaces (One Per Group)

Created at **group creation time** in **PR #11**.

```
Group created
    ↓
Storacha space created: "splitfare-group-{groupId}"
    ↓
Space DID stored in Group.spaceDid column
    ↓
Creator gets full UCAN delegation
```

### What lives inside each group space:

| Content | Who Uploads | Agent | PR |
|---|---|---|---|
| Group avatar | Creator/Admin | Client-side | #11 |
| Expense receipts | Any member | Client-side | #19 |
| Shared media | Any member | Client-side | #38 |
| Settlement manifests | Server (post-settlement) | Server-side | #28 |
| CAR bundles | Server (cron / admin trigger) | Server-side | #33, #35 |

