## UCAN Delegation Model (PR #39)

This is **how access is controlled** per group space:

```
GROUP SPACE: splitfare-group-abc123
│
├── Creator (ADMIN)
│   └── Full delegation (read + write + manage)
│       Granted: on group creation
│
├── Admin members
│   └── Write delegation (read + upload + bundle)
│       Granted: on promotion to admin
│
├── Regular members
│   └── Limited delegation (read + upload receipts/media)
│       Granted: on join
│       Revoked: on leave or removal
│
└── Server agent
    └── Write delegation (manifests + bundles)
        Granted: on group creation
```

### Lifecycle:

```
Member joins group (PR #13)
    → Read + receipt upload delegation granted to member's DID
    → Member can now:
        ✓ Read all content in group space
        ✓ Upload receipts for their expenses
        ✓ Upload shared media

Member leaves / removed (PR #13)
    → Delegation revoked
    → Member can no longer access group space

Member promoted to admin
    → Delegation upgraded to include bundle upload + manage
```

